      <title>纳格尔称欧洲央行不应降息过快，因为尚未达到 2% 的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ecb-mustn-t-cut-too-quickly-as-2-goal-not-reached-nagel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员约阿希姆·纳格尔 (Joachim Nagel) 表示，鉴于通胀率尚未持续回升至 2%，欧洲央行应谨慎降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ecb-mustn-t-cut-too-quickly-as-2-goal-not-reached-nagel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本新日铁呼吁对中国钢铁征收贸易关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/japan-s-nippon-steel-calls-for-trade-tariff-on-chinese-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球第四大钢铁制造商新日本制铁公司表示，日本政府需要对中国钢铁出口征收反倾销关税，以保护国内产业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/japan-s-nippon-steel-calls-for-trade-tariff-on-chinese-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Dollar General 销售描绘了低收入购物者的惨淡前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-29/dollar-general-shows-grim-picture-of-low-income-shoppers-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在折扣零售商 Dollar General 下调全年销售预期后，该公司股价创下有史以来最大跌幅。彭博情报零售日用百货和包装食品高级分析师 Jennifer Bartashus 与彭博情报一起讨论这些数字以及购物者转向哪些商店。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-29/dollar-general-shows-grim-picture-of-low-income-shoppers-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:24:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NFL 的“比尔黑手党”利用市政债券为新体育场提供融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/nfl-s-bills-mafia-tapped-to-finance-new-stadium-with-muni-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布法罗比尔队最忠实的球迷被称为“比尔帮”，他们以向球队伸出援手而闻名，今年早些时候他们清理了 NFL 球队主场的积雪，为季后赛做准备。现在，这些狂热粉丝有机会为球队耗资 17 亿美元的新主场提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/nfl-s-bills-mafia-tapped-to-finance-new-stadium-with-muni-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱迪生达成火灾和解协议后股价创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/edison-hits-all-time-high-after-reaching-fire-settlement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州公用事业公司爱迪生国际公司表示，已与州政府官员达成初步协议，将挽回 2017 年和 2018 年因山火和泥石流造成的近 17 亿美元的损失。此后，该公司股价创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/edison-hits-all-time-high-after-reaching-fire-settlement</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:18:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>力拓、比亚迪等是智利 Enami 锂业的潜在合作伙伴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/rio-tinto-byd-among-prospective-enami-lithium-partners-in-chile-m0fgw5v7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管锂价暴跌，力拓集团与比亚迪股份有限公司仍被选为智利锂资源开发潜在合作伙伴，这也是双方为进一步挖掘全球最大锂资源储量所做出的努力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/rio-tinto-byd-among-prospective-enami-lithium-partners-in-chile-m0fgw5v7</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉美货币领跌新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/emerging-stocks-extend-drop-as-nvidia-dampens-ai-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，拉丁美洲货币下跌，因为新数据显示美国经济走强，推高了美国国债收益率。墨西哥和巴西的政治担忧加剧了这一走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/emerging-stocks-extend-drop-as-nvidia-dampens-ai-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
